<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM14.6">
<l>taruma maṟiyāk kuṟumpaṉait taṅkaic cārṅka matuvēpōl</l>
<l>puruva vaṭṭa maḻakiya porutta miliyaik kaṇṭīrē</l>
<l>uruvu karitāy mukamceytā yutayap paruppa tattiṉmēl</l>
<l>viriyuṅ katirē pōlvāṉai viruntā vaṉattē kaṇṭōmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Did you see the Mischievous One who does not know dharma, the handsome One</l>
<l>—the arch of whose eyebrows are akin to the Cāṛṅkam bow in His hand—</l>
<l rend="indent">who does not associate cordially [with us]?</l>
<l>We saw in Bṛndāvana He who is like the sun that spreads</l>
<l>Above the eastern mountain with the body being dark and the face red!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
